{
  "components": {
    "responses": {},
    "schemas": {
      "DateTime": {
        "description": "Datetime filter values accept UTC ISO 8601 datetimes (e.g. `2024-01-01T00:00:00.000000Z`).\n\n| Operator | Syntax | Description |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| Exact | `value` | Matches the exact datetime |\n| Before | `<value` | Everything before the given datetime |\n| After | `>value` | Everything after the given datetime |\n",
        "title": "DateTime",
        "type": "string"
      },
      "Integer": {
        "description": "Integer filter values match exactly unless a supported operator is provided.\n\n| Operator | Syntax | Description |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| Exact | `value` | Matches the exact value |\n| Less than | `<value` | Values less than given |\n| Greater than | `>value` | Values greater than given |\n| Less than or equal | `<=value` | Values less than or equal to |\n| Greater than or equal | `>=value` | Values greater than or equal to |\n",
        "title": "Integer",
        "type": "string"
      },
      "GroupSort": {
        "enum": [
          "id",
          "insertedAt",
          "name",
          "source",
          "type",
          "idAsc",
          "insertedAtAsc",
          "nameAsc",
          "sourceAsc",
          "typeAsc",
          "idDesc",
          "insertedAtDesc",
          "nameDesc",
          "sourceDesc",
          "typeDesc"
        ],
        "title": "GroupSort",
        "type": "string"
      },
      "DeviceFilter": {
        "description": "Filter devices by one or more fields. Each field type supports different operators.\n\n---\n\n### String Filters\n\nString filter values match exactly unless a supported operator is provided.\n\n| Operator | Syntax | Example | Matches |\n|----------|--------|---------|---------|\n| Exact | `value` | `LAB01` | Equals \"LAB01\" |\n| Starts with | `^value` | `^LAB` | Starts with \"LAB\" |\n| Contains | `~value` | `~server` | Contains \"server\" |\n| Ends with | `value$` | `01$` | Ends with \"01\" |\n\n\n**Applicable fields:** `architecture`, `biosAssetTag`, `biosManufacturer`, `biosVersion`, `chassis`, `currentUser`, `dotNetVersions`, `family`, `hostname`, `lastUser`, `lastUserShortName`, `macAddress`, `manufacturer`, `model`, `name`, `os`, `osFullName`, `osProductType`, `osVersion`, `powershellVersion`, `publicIpAddress`, `serialNumber`, `servicePack`, `sku`, `systemVersion`, `timezone`\n\n---\n\n### Datetime Filters\n\nDatetime filter values accept UTC ISO 8601 datetimes (e.g. `2024-01-01T00:00:00.000000Z`).\n\n| Operator | Syntax | Description |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| Exact | `value` | Matches the exact datetime |\n| Before | `<value` | Everything before the given datetime |\n| After | `>value` | Everything after the given datetime |\n\n\n**Applicable fields:** `insertedAt`, `lastBootUpTime`, `lastSeenAt`, `osInstallDate`, `updatedAt`\n\n---\n\n### Integer Filters\n\nInteger filter values match exactly unless a supported operator is provided.\n\n| Operator | Syntax | Description |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| Exact | `value` | Matches the exact value |\n| Less than | `<value` | Values less than given |\n| Greater than | `>value` | Values greater than given |\n| Less than or equal | `<=value` | Values less than or equal to |\n| Greater than or equal | `>=value` | Values greater than or equal to |\n\n\n**Applicable fields:** `freePercent`, `memory`\n\n---\n\n### Boolean Filters\n\nBoolean filter values accept `true` or `false` strings for exact matching.\n\n\n**Applicable fields:** `requireReboot`, `smbVersionOne`\n",
        "example": {
          "hostname": "~hostname"
        },
        "properties": {
          "timezone": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "smbVersionOne": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Boolean"
          },
          "memory": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Integer"
          },
          "osFullName": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "osVersion": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "customFieldValue": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "os": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "customFieldName": {
            "description": "Filter by custom field name",
            "type": "string"
          },
          "insertedAt": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DateTime"
          },
          "systemVersion": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "lastBootUpTime": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DateTime"
          },
          "servicePack": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "family": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "requireReboot": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Boolean"
          },
          "chassis": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "dotNetVersions": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "currentUser": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "sku": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "biosVersion": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "biosManufacturer": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "biosAssetTag": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "architecture": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "manufacturer": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "lastUser": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "lastSeenAt": {
            "description": "Filter by the last time the device was seen online.\n\nAccepts UTC ISO 8601 datetimes (e.g. `2024-01-01T00:00:00.000000Z`).\n\n**Operators:**\n\n| Prefix | Behavior |\n|--------|----------|\n| `<` | Includes everything before the given datetime |\n| `>` | Includes everything after the given datetime |\n| _(none)_ | Includes everything within ±12 hours of the datetime |\n",
            "type": "string"
          },
          "name": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "powershellVersion": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "freePercent": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Integer"
          },
          "updatedAt": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DateTime"
          },
          "lastUserShortName": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "model": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "publicIpAddress": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "osInstallDate": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DateTime"
          },
          "osProductType": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "hostname": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "macAddress": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          },
          "serialNumber": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/String"
          }
        },
        "title": "DeviceFilter",
        "type": "object"
      },
      "PackageFilter": {
        "description": "String filter values match exactly unless a supported operator is provided.\n\n| Operator | Syntax | Example | Matches |\n|----------|--------|---------|---------|\n| Exact | `value` | `LAB01` | Equals \"LAB01\" |\n| Starts with | `^value` | `^LAB` | Starts with \"LAB\" |\n| Contains | `~value` | `~server` | Contains \"server\" |\n| Ends with | `value$` | `01$` | Ends with \"01\" |\n\n\nValid string filter keys: name, os, publisher, source\n",
        "example": {
          "name": "~name"
