      "GroupFilter": {
        "description": "String filter values match exactly unless a supported operator is provided.\n\n| Operator | Syntax | Example | Matches |\n|----------|--------|---------|---------|\n| Exact | `value` | `LAB01` | Equals \"LAB01\" |\n| Starts with | `^value` | `^LAB` | Starts with \"LAB\" |\n| Contains | `~value` | `~server` | Contains \"server\" |\n| Ends with | `value$` | `01$` | Ends with \"01\" |\n\n\nValid string filter keys: id, name, source, type\n\nDatetime filter values accept UTC ISO 8601 datetimes (e.g. `2024-01-01T00:00:00.000000Z`).\n\n| Operator | Syntax | Description |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| Exact | `value` | Matches the exact datetime |\n| Before | `<value` | Everything before the given datetime |\n| After | `>value` | Everything after the given datetime |\n\n\nValid filter keys: insertedAt\n",
