          },
          {
            "description": "String filter values match exactly unless a supported operator is provided.\n\n| Operator | Syntax | Example | Matches |\n|----------|--------|---------|---------|\n| Exact | `value` | `LAB01` | Equals \"LAB01\" |\n| Starts with | `^value` | `^LAB` | Starts with \"LAB\" |\n| Contains | `~value` | `~server` | Contains \"server\" |\n| Ends with | `value$` | `01$` | Ends with \"01\" |\n\n\nValid string filter keys: name, os, publisher, source\n",
            "in": "query",
            "name": "filter",
